The paper deals with communication complexity, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The use of Kolmogorov complexity suggests a connection to data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.DM). Finally, the consideration of different types of protocols and the use of help bits suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
